#!/bin/sh
# Auto-stamp the module cache-buster so a changed standalone/js/*.js module can
# never be served stale. Restages index.html if the stamp changed. Lenient by
# design — if node is unavailable it skips rather than blocking the commit.
#
# Activate once per clone:  git config core.hooksPath .githooks
command -v node >/dev/null 2>&1 || exit 0
node scripts/stamp-cache-bust.js || exit 0
git add standalone/index.html 2>/dev/null || true
exit 0
